  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Raising your weapon and slamming it on the ground, you shake the very ground beneath your feet. All targets in range must make a Dexterity saving throw against either your Ninjutsu or Taijutsu Save DC (whichever is higher) or be knocked prone and take 3d4 fire damage as small gouts of fire burst from beneath them. If this jutsu is used again on targets that are already prone, those targets must make this save at disadvantage, and on a failure take 2d8 fire damage and gain 2 ranks of the Burned condition.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you upcast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the range by 30 feet.</p>",
